"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把野可以講<br />\n就咁完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世界意志咁就輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a8fbffab27ba2169db9eebdf826028a91bd4b7","tid":488723,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把野可以講<br />\n就咁完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想知艾德魯救唔救得番<br />\n希望單行本有加頁<br />\n不過真係完得好完美<br />\n艾莉西亞黨超滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5fd7a287ba09623d37fc8aca8009e6c03004c6","tid":488723,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似同jump一樣玩每週排名？<br />\n係咪成績太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀 排名其實都好前<br />\n<br />\n可能真係講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661b51c37bc1450485fbbf772d9b35c5b8bd71e8","tid":488723,"uid":150544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"咁未幾好, 係必需既時候完就完<br />\n唔好次次一完就話人係斬咁膚淺啦<br />\n大隻佬個故事都無咩好再講, 條女又救返<br />\n要講都係其他角色既後日談<br />\n唔係話要死拖難拖先叫好"},{"pid":"b277231bc71b4f02790e84b2f742202774308c89","tid":488723,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"來完咪完 唔係有世界觀就要講哂嘅<br />\n我覺得完得好完美<br />\n<br />\n你睇返大劍 都係仲有兩個大帝國嘅戰爭無講<br />\n但係其實無必要講囉<br />\n個故事都完咗<br />\n留返啲想像空間俾讀者<br />\n等啲角色係故事完咗之後都繼續活係心入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS 安妮真係超萌 赫魯庫唔要就留返俾我"},{"pid":"89461d1238f71a56a214d4e35ac194702c9021fe","tid":488723,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ec739b686f953fa76751f4de9b326f19ab883c","tid":488723,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來完咪完 唔係有世界觀就要講哂嘅<br />\n我覺得完得好完美<br />\n<br />\n你睇返大劍 都係仲有兩個大帝國嘅戰爭無講<br />\n但係其實無必要講囉<br />\n個故事都完咗<br />\n留返啲想像空間俾讀者<br />\n等啲角色係故事完咗之後都繼續活係心入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS 安妮真係超萌 赫魯庫唔要就留返俾我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁快完應該係打完講多兩頁就完？<br />\n咁我覺得快左少少<br />\n虐左咁耐（女友走果2幕真係虐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n打完大戰都俾多2話甜下啦<br />\n打完就結局有啲意猶未盡"},{"pid":"84c24fe637c0416eaa6b7b831804b15067f99cb1","tid":488723,"uid":150544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>來完咪完 唔係有世界觀就要講哂嘅<br />\n我覺得完得好完美<br />\n<br />\n你睇返大劍 都係仲有兩個大帝國嘅戰爭無講<br />\n但係其實無必要講囉<br />\n個故事都完咗<br />\n留返啲想像空間俾讀者<br />\n等啲角色係故事完咗之後都繼續活係心入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS 安妮真係超萌 赫魯庫唔要就留返俾我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁快完應該係打完講多兩頁就完？<br />\n咁我覺得快左少少<br />\n虐左咁耐（女友走果2幕真係虐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n打完大戰都俾多2話甜下啦<br />\n打完就結局有啲意猶未盡</blockquote><br />\n搞到咁甜又有人講虐安妮黨<br />\n本身大隻佬同個女仔都係寫到咁露骨<br />\n咁樣淡淡然小甜最好"},{"pid":"4b1cdd6d7866c19cdcd8c7197a4053c6de2b7786","tid":488723,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"不得不說 完得好靚<br />\n但個最終戰就一般般 如果唔計最終戰~成套漫令人覺得輕鬆搞笑幾過引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc7f46502837cd13d0a0070c36f01cabbb9d491","tid":488723,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不得不說 完得好靚<br />\n但個最終戰就一般般 如果唔計最終戰~成套漫令人覺得輕鬆搞笑幾過引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終戰打左勁耐，出完呢隻又出果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1e670a8a4c2932cdad64518b294c40424de4a1","tid":488723,"uid":49293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"四天王剩係出左兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cc68950fca7e3871044f13da43e909250ea713","tid":488723,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be254a6535cc1c46c8577176b33187396ba462c3","tid":488723,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不得不說 完得好靚<br />\n但個最終戰就一般般 如果唔計最終戰~成套漫令人覺得輕鬆搞笑幾過引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終戰打左勁耐，出完呢隻又出果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都輕鬆搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好沉重喎<br />\n只係作者用最輕鬆嘅手法嚟表達"},{"pid":"0bfb9dbd26359cee58ec73f36ecc653f31a98401","tid":488723,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不得不說 完得好靚<br />\n但個最終戰就一般般 如果唔計最終戰~成套漫令人覺得輕鬆搞笑幾過引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終戰打左勁耐，出完呢隻又出果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都輕鬆搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好沉重喎<br />\n只係作者用最輕鬆嘅手法嚟表達</blockquote><br />\n前期幽默 中期沉重 後期就兩樣一齊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最終戰假如一次過睇會好爽"},{"pid":"bbbdced6ccfbb778f98220dcf311f848b4cf8ea7","tid":488723,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大把野可以講<br />\n就咁完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世界意志咁就輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>無輸<br />\n最後一定update到世界"},{"pid":"e13069150ece34d62f24bf0a706c5254573b0ea2","tid":488723,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"睇返赫魯庫一開頭個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同依家對比好似整左容咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5386ef27d23e6793c02148953d4ebcbabf573968","tid":488723,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇返赫魯庫一開頭個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同依家對比好似整左容咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人話因爲套漫係安妮視角，最開始係麻煩友所以佢眼中就係傻仔樣，後來一步步親密就一步步變靚仔，其實都幾講得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0878fb3fad84238fdc5a8d803db5a82b01850ebf","tid":488723,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇返赫魯庫一開頭個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同依家對比好似整左容咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人話因爲套漫係安妮視角，最開始係麻煩友所以佢眼中就係傻仔樣，後來一步步親密就一步步變靚仔，其實都幾講得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/forum/w%3D315.20000000000005%3Bq%3D80%3Bg%3D0/sign=cab0f3e0b83533faf5b6952f9dfdcf2f/da8df7dda3cc7cd95e784e373001213fb90e91ae.jpg?&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fda8df7dda3cc7cd95e784e373001213fb90e91ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D315.20000000000005%253Bq%253D80%253Bg%253D0%2Fsign%3Dcab0f3e0b83533faf5b6952f9dfdcf2f%2Fda8df7dda3cc7cd95e784e373001213fb90e91ae.jpg%3F%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimgsrc.baidu.com%252Fforum%252Fpic%252Fitem%252Fda8df7dda3cc7cd95e784e373001213fb90e91ae.jpg&h=c422b6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/forum/w%3D315.20000000000005%3Bq%3D80%3Bg%3D0/sign=4d64ebd142fbfbeddc59307e4ddec506/d1a410177f3e6709def63f1132c79f3df9dc5508.jpg?&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fd1a410177f3e6709def63f1132c79f3df9dc5508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D315.20000000000005%253Bq%253D80%253Bg%253D0%2Fsign%3D4d64ebd142fbfbeddc59307e4ddec506%2Fd1a410177f3e6709def63f1132c79f3df9dc5508.jpg%3F%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimgsrc.baidu.com%252Fforum%252Fpic%252Fitem%252Fd1a410177f3e6709def63f1132c79f3df9dc5508.jpg&h=b766cf27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左幾多轉韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabb50ee46d55646b4347217d4c258b76b8d002e","tid":488723,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大把野可以講<br />\n就咁完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世界意志咁就輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>無輸<br />\n最後一定update到世界</blockquote><br />\n赫魯庫話打贏嘅只係世界意志嘅超小一部份<br />\n<br />\n不過都有話 俾世界意志干涉嘅人只要有人幫手<br />\n就有機會可以控制到自己<br />\n如果可以咁樣搵多幾個赫魯庫咁勁嘅世界意志接觸者入team<br />\n都仲可能有方法嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}